This module displays all sub-menus of the page where it is used and has 
some configuration settings that change its behaviour.

Check out its Wiki page at: 
<a href="http://wiki.bigace.de/bigace:extensions:modul:submenupreview" target="_blank">http://wiki.bigace.de/bigace:extensions:modul:submenupreview</a>

Version 1.3:
------------
- added flag to display pages in "reverse order"
- using path constant instead of global variable to protect against XSS